Randall D. Mott



Mr. Randall D. Mott is Chief Information Officer & Senior Vice President at General Motors Co. He is on the Board of Directors at Dun & Bradstreet Corp.
Mr. Mott was previously employed as Chief Information Officer & Executive VP by Hewlett-Packard Co., Chief Information Officer & Senior Vice President by Dell, Inc., and Chief Information Officer & Senior Vice President by Wal-Mart Stores, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from The University of Arkansas.



